{{Databox|en=Tarifit}}Tga '''Tarifit''' awal amaziɣ nna s sawaln ayt [[rrif]]. Zɣ mad nufa ɣ usiḍn amrrukiy n 2004, uṭṭun n imssiwln n trifiyt ɣ [[Lmɣrib|umrruk]] iga t attayn n 1,270,000 umlyun, ilkm attayn n 1,5 umlyun ɣ umaḍal akkʷ. zɣ dar isugam yaḍnin, ittwasitg wuṭṭun n imssiwln nns s wattayn n 3 imlyunn.

Llan tuggt n imssiwln n trifiyt ɣ [[Urupa|urubba]] nna s ddan dffir n uzwag nnsn imqqurn zɣ wammas n isggʷasn n 1960. [[Hulanḍa]], [[Bljika|Abljik]], d [[Lalman|Waliman]], gan timizar nna ɣ bahra llan.

Waxxa ittwassn ism ad n "tarifiyt", ig yan yirm ubɣir (ilan abɣur), imaziɣn n rrif ar aqqran i tutlayt-nnsn s ism "tamaziɣt".

Tiqbilin timslmaziɣin nna isawaln s trifiyt gan tnt: ibqquyn, ayt uryaɣl, ayt tmsaman, ayt tuzin, ayt ɛmmart, [[igznnayn]], (mtalsa, ibdarsn?), ayt sɛid, iqlɛiyn, tafrsit, ayt Oulicek(?), ayt buyḥyi, ikbdanen, ayt gmil.

== Isnfiln Imsislitn ==
